# Accessibility Standards (v0.1.13)

## Core Requirements
- WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliance
- Full keyboard navigation
- Screen reader optimization
- Focus management with Next.js App Router
- Video/media accessibility

## Component Standards
```typescript
{
  "accessibilityStandards": {
    "components": {
      "basic": {
        "images": { 
          "alt": "required",
          "loading": "lazy" 
        },
        "forms": { 
          "labels": "required",
          "aria": "required" 
        },
        "buttons": { 
          "role": "required",
          "ariaLabel": "required" 
        },
        "video": {
          "controls": "optional",
          "autoplay": "allowed",
          "loop": "allowed",
          "muted": "required",
          "playsInline": "required"
        }
      },
      "navigation": {
        "keyboard": true,
        "skipLinks": true,
        "landmarks": true
      }
    },
    "testing": {
      "tools": ["axe-core", "jest-axe"],
      "frequency": "continuous"
    }
  }
}
```